OL,3,C'Change is difficult': Welsh farmers
OL,4,Cwarned to be 'patient' on subsidy
OL,5,Cscheme
OL,7,FIn my first interview with the new
OL,8,Fcabinet minister for Rural Resilience
OL,9,Fand Sustainability Llyr Gruffydd MS he
OL,10,Facknowledged that "change is
OL,11,Fdifficult" when it comes to reforms in
OL,12,Frural Wales and farming, but has
OL,13,Fwarned that "the cost of not acting
OL,14,Fnow on some of these issues will cost
OL,15,Fus even more in future."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/16
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
