FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1779797464
OL,3,C'Change is difficult': Welsh farmers
OL,4,Cwarned to be 'patient' on subsidy
OL,5,Cscheme
OL,7,FThis was my first chance to sit down
OL,8,Fwith Mr Gruffydd since coming into the
OL,9,Frole last week, and I asked him to
OL,10,Faddress two big issues in his in-tray:
OL,11,Fthe ongoing row about the construction
OL,12,Fof large steel pylons in the Welsh
OL,13,Fcountryside and getting farmers on
OL,14,Fboard with the Sustainable Farming
OL,15,FScheme.
OL,17,FThe development of a 60-mile-long
OL,18,Fnetwork of new pylons between Powys
OL,19,Fand Carmarthenshire has been earmarked
OL,20,Fto increase national grid capacity, as
OL,21,FWales generates more renewable energy.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/16
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1779797464
OL,3,C'Change is difficult': Welsh farmers
OL,4,Cwarned to be 'patient' on subsidy
OL,5,Cscheme
OL,7,FBut campaigners have long called for
OL,8,Fnew electric cables to be buried
OL,9,Funderground instead of building new
OL,10,Fpylon infrastructure.
OL,12,FMr Gruffydd said he "absolutely
OL,13,Funderstand(s) people's concerns,"
OL,14,Fsaying Plaid Cymru were clear in their
OL,15,Fmanifesto commitment in terms of
OL,16,Fundergrounding where possible, but
OL,17,Falso moving away from the steel
OL,18,Flattice pilots.
OL,26,@uD@KpmuD@Mpn
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/16
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1779797464
OL,3,C'Change is difficult': Welsh farmers
OL,4,Cwarned to be 'patient' on subsidy
OL,5,Cscheme
OL,7,FIn their election manifesto, Plaid
OL,8,FCymru said they would "immediately
OL,9,Fprohibit the use of large steel
OL,10,Flattice pylons," and campaigners say
OL,11,Fthat the new government will now be
OL,12,Funder pressure to stick to their
OL,13,Fmanifesto commitments.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/16
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1779797464
OL,3,C'Change is difficult': Welsh farmers
OL,4,Cwarned to be 'patient' on subsidy
OL,5,Cscheme
OL,7,FMr Gruffydd said that it was
OL,8,Fultimately a matter for his cabinet
OL,9,Fcolleague, the Energy Minister Adam
OL,10,FPrice, but added: "We're on it and we
OL,11,Fwill be true to our manifesto that
OL,12,Fwill be reflected, I hope, in some of
OL,13,Fthe decisions that my fellow ministers
OL,14,Fmake."
OL,16,FStella Price is a farmer in Powys, who
OL,17,Fhas taken part in protests against new
OL,18,Fpylons on her land. She says that the
OL,19,Fnew Plaid Cymru government now have to
OL,20,Fdeliver on their election promises.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/16
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1779797464
OL,3,C'Change is difficult': Welsh farmers
OL,4,Cwarned to be 'patient' on subsidy
OL,5,Cscheme
OL,7,F"Of course underground is an essential
OL,8,Fask, but it's one of many asks.
OL,10,F"It's the scale that is worrying a lot
OL,11,Fof rural people at the moment. I think
OL,12,Fthe best solution that we can have is
OL,13,Fa pause and a consultation period.
OL,15,F"That's what we want to ask Plaid
OL,16,FCymru to do: consult the rural
OL,17,Fcommunities that this is affecting,
OL,18,Flook at a better way of taking this
OL,19,Fforward, and engage properly."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/16
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1779797464
OL,3,C'Change is difficult': Welsh farmers
OL,4,Cwarned to be 'patient' on subsidy
OL,5,Cscheme
OL,7,FMeanwhile, many others in rural Wales
OL,8,Fhave also protested against the
OL,9,Fprevious Welsh Labour Government's
OL,10,Fflagship Sustainable Farming Scheme,
OL,11,Fwhich was finally introduced earlier
OL,12,Fthis year after months of widespread
OL,13,Fdemonstrations.
OL,15,FThe scheme is designed to replace the
OL,16,Ffunding for Welsh farmers previously
OL,17,Fgiven by the European Union.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/16
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1779797464
OL,3,C'Change is difficult': Welsh farmers
OL,4,Cwarned to be 'patient' on subsidy
OL,5,Cscheme
OL,7,FSo far the uptake of the new scheme is
OL,8,Fsaid to be low, and it is the new
OL,9,FPlaid Cymru Welsh Government that will
OL,10,Fbe responsible for encouraging better
OL,11,Fuptake or changing the scheme
OL,12,Faltogether.
OL,14,FI asked the new cabinet minister just
OL,15,Fhow many farmers had signed up to the
OL,16,Fso-called SFS in the first few months.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/16
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1779797464
OL,3,C'Change is difficult': Welsh farmers
OL,4,Cwarned to be 'patient' on subsidy
OL,5,Cscheme
OL,7,F"Well it's early days, officials are
OL,8,Fstill working through the figures, but
OL,9,Fas a rule of thumb, broadly we can say
OL,10,Fthat it's about 50-50 split in terms
OL,11,Fof numbers of applications," Llyr
OL,12,FGruffydd said.
OL,14,F"I've always said I've been on the
OL,15,Fsame page as the farming unions when
OL,16,Fit comes to the SFS so far. We have a
OL,17,Fscheme. It's far from perfect. It
OL,18,Fneeds improving, and that's the work
OL,19,Fthat's already begun.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/16
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1779797464
OL,3,C'Change is difficult': Welsh farmers
OL,4,Cwarned to be 'patient' on subsidy
OL,5,Cscheme
OL,7,F"Some of those changes maybe could be
OL,8,Fintroduced pretty quickly. Others
OL,9,Fmight need more significant change, so
OL,10,Fpeople will need to be a little bit
OL,11,Fpatient.
OL,13,F"I've been enrolled for literally
OL,14,Fdays, but it's certainly close to the
OL,15,Ftop of my list in terms of the work
OL,16,Fthat we need to do."
OL,18,FBut responding to the interview, Welsh
OL,19,FConservative Shadow Farming Minister
OL,20,FAndrew RT Davies said the cabinet
OL,21,Fminister lacked urgency.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/16
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1779797464
OL,3,C'Change is difficult': Welsh farmers
OL,4,Cwarned to be 'patient' on subsidy
OL,5,Cscheme
OL,7,FMr Davies said: "If the will is there,
OL,8,Fthere's no reason reforms can't be
OL,9,Fimplemented immediately.J"Plaid Cymru
OL,10,Fseparatists must fulfil their promises
OL,11,Fto Welsh farmers now."
OL,13,FJethro Small from Upper Chapel near
OL,14,FBrecon is one farmer who has refused
OL,15,Fto join the scheme. He said the
OL,16,Fcurrent scheme asks farmers to
OL,17,Fincrease costs and workloads whilst
OL,18,Fpayments go down.
OL,26,@qD@ZOUsD@VO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/16
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1779797464
OL,3,C'Change is difficult': Welsh farmers
OL,4,Cwarned to be 'patient' on subsidy
OL,5,Cscheme
OL,7,FWhen I asked Jethro how a new Plaid
OL,8,FCymru administration could tempt him
OL,9,Fto join the scheme, he said a big part
OL,10,Fwas scrapping the basic requirements
OL,11,Fneeded to sign up.
OL,13,F"The worst part about it is these
OL,14,Funiversal actions. Every action comes
OL,15,Fwith a cost and extra paperwork and
OL,16,Fit's taking money from the farm income.
OL,18,F"We can't afford these extra costs and
OL,19,Fwe haven't got the time to do all this
OL,20,Fextra paperwork."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/16
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1779797464
OL,3,C'Change is difficult': Welsh farmers
OL,4,Cwarned to be 'patient' on subsidy
OL,5,Cscheme
OL,7,F"I think they've (Plaid Cymru) got
OL,8,Fquite a short window to show that they
OL,9,Fare on the farmers' side to try and
OL,10,Faddress all these problems with this
OL,11,Fscheme, if they want to regain trust."
OL,13,FThe generation of more cleaner greener
OL,14,Fenergy in Wales, and the delivery of
OL,15,Fclimate change and biodiversity
OL,16,Ftargets have also been Plaid Cymru
OL,17,Fpromises.
OL,26,@oD@RpmoD@^pn
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G13/16
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1779797464
OL,3,C'Change is difficult': Welsh farmers
OL,4,Cwarned to be 'patient' on subsidy
OL,5,Cscheme
OL,7,FMr Gruffydd pointed out that some of
OL,8,Fthose targets are a legal requirement,
OL,9,Fand that the cost of not acting on
OL,10,Fsome of these issues will cost more in
OL,11,Ffuture, for example, with climate
OL,12,Fchange set to bring drought, hot
OL,13,Fweather, and flooding that's having an
OL,14,Fimpact on farming already.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G14/16
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46615
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1779797464
OL,3,C'Change is difficult': Welsh farmers
OL,4,Cwarned to be 'patient' on subsidy
OL,5,Cscheme
OL,7,F"It's all about creating a more viable
OL,8,Ffarming sector that, as a consequence,
OL,9,Fprovides us with greater food
OL,10,Fsecurity, but in order to do that, our
OL,11,Ffarming industry needs to become
OL,12,Fclimate resilient. They go hand in
OL,13,Fhand for me.
OL,15,F"People see them as contradictory
OL,16,Ftensions pulling in different
OL,17,Fdirections. I don't, but there is a
OL,18,Fcareful route to be steered along that
OL,19,Fin terms of making sure it works for
OL,20,Fboth."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G15/16
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,467,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46616
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1779797464
OL,3,C'Change is difficult': Welsh farmers
OL,4,Cwarned to be 'patient' on subsidy
OL,5,Cscheme
OL,7,FBut the challenge for the party and
OL,8,Fthe new Welsh Government will be how
OL,9,Fthey can reach their goals on these
OL,10,Fambitions, and satisfy rural voters
OL,11,Fthat they will do so without having a
OL,12,Fnegative impact on their lives and
OL,13,Flivelihoods.
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G16/16
